.\" termin.al-name: cd
.\" termin.al-usage: cd [path]
.\" termin.al-summary: Change this shell pane's virtual directory.
.TH CD 1 "" "termin.al" "termin.al Manual"
.ftr B R
.ftr I R
.ftr BI R
.SH NAME
cd \- Change this shell pane's virtual directory.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
cd [path]
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
Changes the working directory owned by the current shell pane. Each pane keeps its own directory, so moving in one pane does not move another.
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
$ cd projects
$ cd ..
.fi
.SH SEE ALSO
help(1), man(1)
